data.title: Jean Jacques Annaud: Movies, Photos, Videos, News, Biography & Birthday
data.meta_description: Jean Jacques Annaud: Check out the list of all Jean Jacques Annaud movies along with photos, videos, biography and birthday. Also find latest Jean Jacques Annaud news on Times of India.
data.text:
French director Jean-Jacques Annaud sourced actual footage of Notre-Dame blaze for his film

IANS / Jun 10, 2022, 12:40 (IST)

The makers of 'Notre-Dame On Fire' left no stone unturned to lend authenticity to the film which captures the blaze that took place at the historic Notre-Dame cathedral and tells the story of many courageous souls who risked everything to douse the deadly flames.

“French filmmaker Jean-Jacques Annaud is my inspiration”: Goodachari director Sashi Kiran Tikka lists his favourite films

TIMESOFINDIA.COM / Mar 26, 2020, 19:34 (IST)

In an exclusive conversation with E Times, Sashi Kiran said “Jean-Jacques Annaud is my inspiration to become a director. His films like ‘Bear’ and ‘Enemy at the Gates’ are my all-time favourite.”

Patrick Dempsey lands first TV role after 'Grey's Anatomy'

PTI / Aug 16, 2017, 13:22 (IST)

The 51-year-old actor will star in Epix's series "The Truth About the Harry Quebert Affair", based on Joel Dicker's novel of the same name, reports aceshowbiz.com.

Arnold Schwarzenegger to address Beijing film festival?

PTI / Apr 12, 2015, 16:58 (IST)

Austrian-born US actor and former California governor Arnold Schwarzenegger will attend and address the fifth Beijing International Film Festival, to begin from April 16.

Anushka Sharma to attend the screening of NH10 at Beijing International Film Festival

PTI / Apr 15, 2015, 13:49 (IST)

Bollywood actress Anushka Sharma will attend the screening of her movie NH10 here in the 5th Beijing International Film Festival to be held from April 17-20.

NFAI to get 230 French films

TNN / Apr 30, 2009, 03:43 (IST)

The National Film Archive of India's (NFAI) collection of films is all set to grow as it gets ready to receive more than 230 French films from the French embassy on April 30.

Freida, Riz to star together in 'Trishna'

TNN / Feb 16, 2011, 11:22 (IST)

Freida Pinto and Riz Ahmed to do Michael Winterbottom's adaptation of Tess of the d'Urbervilles titled 'Trishna' about the relationship between a property dealer and the daughter of an autorickshaw owner.

From 'Roman Holiday' to 'The Darjeeling Limited': Most memorable travel-themed films

TNN / Sep 27, 2015, 16:48 (IST)

It’s quite magical how films, more than any other piece of pop-culture ephemera, have the power to sweep you away on a Mediterranean cruise, walk you into the lap of the Alps or whisk you through a musty flea market in Asia.
